<%= render :partial => 'o_cms/images/navigation' %>

<h2>New Image</h2>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <p>Guidelines for images</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Make sure you include a name for your image.</li>
      <li>Make sure the file type is an image file type e.g. gif, jpg, png.</li>
      <li>Description is optional but will be used when you embed or use the image.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { image: @image } %>
  </div>
</div>
